## ğŸš€ Features

### âœ¨ Core Capabilities

- **Multilingual NLP**: Handles Hindi, English, and code-mixed conversations
- **Real-time Sentiment**: Analyzes product mentions with 75%+ accuracy
- **Demand Forecasting**: Predicts sentiment trends 14 days ahead
- **Interactive Dashboard**: Beautiful Plotly visualizations
- **Explainable AI**: SHAP values for model interpretability

### ğŸ“Š Analytics

- Sentiment distribution analysis
- Daily post volume tracking
- Subreddit-wise trends
- Confidence scoring
- Forecast accuracy metrics

